Enum Class CommandType

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<CommandType>
netpbm.command.CommandType
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<CommandType>, Constable
public enum CommandType extends Enum<CommandType>
Lists all available command types in the image editor. Each command is identified by a keyword typed in the console.
